
Maintenance

(1)
stop mysqld on master side

(2)
run STOP SLAVE IO_THREAD on all slaves
check SHOW PROCESSLIST => Has read all relay log

(3)
run STOP SLAVE RESET MASTER on new master

(4)
run STOP SLAVE and CHANGE MASTER TO MASTER_HOST='new master IP(hostname)' on all salves except new master
run START SLAVE

(5)
change mysql configuration on application side

(6)
"change old master as new slave"
run  RESET MASTER
run  CHANGE MASTER TO MASTER_HOST='new master IP(hostname)'




